    "description": {
      "description": "<p>Arremesso, Receita</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\">No contato a Granada de Ondas Radioativas [GORA] explode liberando ondas de energia radioativa em uma sequência de dois pulsos.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Uso:</span> Arremesso.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo de preparo:</span> 1 ação.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Alcance:</span> 7/21m.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Área:</span> raio de 3m.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Dano:</span> 12+COG<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-family:Arial\">×2</span> de dano Biológico: Podre</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Efeitos:</span> ao fim da rodada, causa o [Dano] uma segunda vez.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Preço:</span> 6 pratas.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Ofício:</span> Engenharia N7.</p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Tempo para fabricar:</span><span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:9.0pt;line-height:105%\"> 12 horas.</span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-indent:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:8.5pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;line-height:105%\">Materiais:</span> 1 de Metal e 1 de Eônio<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-size:8.0pt;line-height:105%;mso-fareast